Subject: Can't download current version
Description: while trying to download the latest release I encountered the same error from last time. Can you please provide a functional downloadlink for me? I need to update our version of pingcastle.
Solution_Comment__c:
As part of the recent updates to the My Products Tool admin panel, dev team modified the logic for downloading the PingCastle license which caused this error.

This was resolved by the web team and user has signed off.
